<div class="relative">
  <div style="background-image: linear-gradient(-180deg, #FFFFFF 0%, #F4F6F9 100%)">
    <div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">
      <div class="h-2 bg-purple"></div>
      <main class="flex-1">
        <div class="hero border-b">
          <nav class="w-full max-w-screen mx-auto px-68 py-8 md:px-12">
            <div class="text-center md:flex md:justify-between md:items-center">
              <h2>Poe Currency Log</h2>
              <div class="hidden md:flex">
                <%= link_to 'Login', new_user_session_path, class: "font-bold uppercase no-underline text-black hover:text-grey-dark"  %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </nav>

          <div class="w-full max-w-screen mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="py-8 text-center">
              <h1 class="text-black text-4xl font-bold mb-6 leading-none md:text-6xl">
                Your league currency progression in charts
              </h1>
              <p class="text-grey-dark mx-auto text-lg max-w-md md:text-2xl">
                With automatic logging you will have one more reason to grind and show your friends how rich you are.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto flex">
              <%= image_tag("screenshot.png", class: "self-end px-4") %>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center py-6 hidden md:block">
              <p class="text-lg text-black">
                It's <strong>FREE</strong> but I am accepting donations.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="max-w-md mx-auto mb-8 w-1/6">
              <div class="bg-purple-dark hover:bg-purple text-white text-2xl font-bold py-3 rounded shadow-md cursor-pointer uppercase text-center tracking-wide">
                Sign up now
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-black text-grey">
          <div class="w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto py-20">
            <!-- <div class="text-sm uppercase text-center font-semibold tracking-wider mb-1 md:text-md">
              Why you should choose PingPing
            </div> -->
            <div class="text-2xl text-center font-semibold mb-20 md:text-3xl uppercase">
              Features so far
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
              <div class="w-full flex flex-col text-center mb-10 px-8 md:flex-row md:text-left md:w-1/2">
                <!-- <div class="mb-4 md:mb-0">
                  icon
                </div> -->
                <div class="flex-1 text-lg md:pl-10">
                  <div class="font-bold text-xl mb-4">
                    Automatic logging
                  </div>
                    <p class="text-grey-darker">
                      Grind in peace exile! <br>
                      Every 6h the system will fetch for updates and automatically.
                    </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="w-full flex flex-col text-center mb-10 px-8 md:flex-row md:text-left md:w-1/2">
                <!-- <div class="mb-4 md:mb-0">
                  icon
                </div> -->
                <div class="flex-1 text-lg md:pl-10">
                  <div class="font-bold text-xl mb-4">
                    Progression charts
                  </div>
                    <p class="text-grey-darker">
                      All data
                    </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
              <div class="w-full flex flex-col text-center mb-10 px-8 md:flex-row md:text-left md:w-1/2">
                <!-- <div class="mb-4 md:mb-0">
                  icon
                </div> -->
                <div class="flex-1 text-lg md:pl-10">
                  <div class="font-bold text-xl mb-4">
                    Privacy and security
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-grey-darker">
                    The system encrypts your session and will never publish any data collected
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="w-full flex flex-col text-center px-8 md:flex-row md:text-left md:w-1/2">
                <!-- <div class="mb-4 md:mb-0">
                  icon
                </div> -->
                <div class="flex-1 text-lg md:pl-10">
                  <div class="font-bold text-xl mb-4">
                    Hidden statistics
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-grey-darker">
                    Ever wondered how was your progression last league in comparison with the current one? Wonder no more!
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-grey-darkest">
          <div class="w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto py-20 md:px-12">
            <div class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-10 md:text-3xl uppercase">
              Questions you may have
            </div>

            <div class="block md:flex leading-normal py-6">
              <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg text-white font-bold w:full md:w-1/3 pr-0 md:pr-3 mb-4 m:mb-0">
                Why is this free?
              </h3>
              <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-blue-lighter w:full md:w-2/3 pl-0 md:pl-3">
                This application was built entirely for learning purposes, I am a developer, so the intuit here is to maintain a performatic application with the lowest cost possible.
                <br>
                If you feel generous enough, you can donate to me, I will appreciate a lot.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="block md:flex leading-normal py-6">
              <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg text-white font-bold w:full md:w-1/3 pr-0 md:pr-3 mb-4 m:mb-0">
                Why my session is needed?
              </h3>
              <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-blue-lighter w:full md:w-2/3 pl-0 md:pl-3">
                Have you ever used Currency Cop before? It's for the same reason.<br>
                We don't have an API for fetching your private stashes, that's the only reason the session is needed.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="block md:flex leading-normal py-6">
              <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg text-white font-bold w:full md:w-1/3 pr-0 md:pr-3 mb-4 m:mb-0">
                Can you see my session id?
              </h3>
              <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-blue-lighter w:full md:w-2/3 pl-0 md:pl-3">
                Nope! Your poe session is encrypted at the sign up and it will never be used outside this application.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="block md:flex leading-normal py-6">
              <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg text-white font-bold w:full md:w-1/3 pr-0 md:pr-3 mb-4 m:mb-0">
                Can you see my data?
              </h3>
              <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-blue-lighter w:full md:w-2/3 pl-0 md:pl-3">
                No, your data is secured with your email and password, that is also encrypted at sign up, and no one without the password can access it.
              </p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
      <footer class="bg-purple-dark">
        <div class="w-full max-w-screen mx-auto px-66 py-6 text-sm text-grey md:px-12">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:justify-between">
            <ul class="list-reset flex flex-col text-center mb-6 md:text-left md:mb-0">
              <li>
                Built by <a href="https://twitter.com/fladsongomes" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferer" class="no-underline font-bold text-white hover:underline">@fladsongomes</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="list-reset flex flex-col text-center md:flex-row md:text-left">
              <li class="md:mr-6"><a href="#" class="no-underline text-white hover:underline">Terms and conditions</a></li>
              <li class="md:mr-6"><a href="#" class="no-underline text-white hover:underline">Privacy policy</a></li>
              <!-- <li><a href="#" class="no-underline text-white hover:underline">Imprint</a></li> -->
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
